message.body: Hey babe, I got a question for you. So that weekend, are you trying to just go there for the night and relax or are you trying to have a party? Or are you just having a little get together for whoever wants to come spend the night...orrrrrrr....? What ya thinkin?
Yea it's small I think Jess is coming but i didn't invite people just threw it out to whoever asked me what my plans were
I mean you can invite Danielle but I'm not trying to have it be too crazy
Ok cool. I feel ya fo sho. Quiet is nice. I look forward to hanging with you guys!
Us too! Blakslee is gonna come Saturday night too
